criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  ≥18 years

          -  type 2 diabetics

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  malignancy;

          -  severe cardiovascular complications;

          -  any history of chronic hepatitis (hepatitis B or C virus infection, autoimmune
             hepatitis, Wilson's disease, hemachromatosis);

          -  secondary causes of fatty liver ( glucocorticoids, amiodarone, tamoxifen);

          -  alcohol consuming (20grams per day for male, and 10 grams per day for female);

          -  any hints of type 1 diabetes ( ketoacidosis, ketonuria, using insulin within 1 year
             after diagnosis)
